  <brief_title>Trial to Compare the Relative Pharmacodynamic Properties of Different Glucagon Dosages</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomised, Single Center, Three-period Trial to Compare the Relative Pharmacodynamic Properties of Different Glucagon Dosages at Four Different Blood Glucose Concentrations</official_title>
  <sponsors>
